author: rdonkin
msg: Created simple parser for jar MANIFESTs. Aim is to extract lists of header names to run audit rules against. So opted for simple heuristic to extract names rather than to generate complete parser.

author: davsclaus
msg: CAMEL-4233: Improved how type converters is loaded. Added support for specifying FQN in META-INF TypeConverter file to load the Converter class directly, avoiding package scanning. This speedup startup process, and makes Camel able to run in other environments without the need for package scanning.
